data.description: ***Price Improvement** Nestled in the heart of Alberhill, this exquisite Lake Elsinore residence features 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms across a spacious 2,969 square feet. Lavishly upgraded, the home boasts an inviting open floor-plan. As you enter, the dining and living rooms showcase tile flooring and wood floors. To the left, a hallway leads to a downstairs bedroom and a full bathroom with a shower. The expansive kitchen is a culinary haven, with abundant cabinets, ample storage, a vast kitchen island with a deep sink, and exquisite granite countertops. Double sliding doors seamlessly connect the kitchen and family room to the backyard.The family room is bathed in natural light, enhanced by windows, a media niche, and a gas fireplace. Upstairs, discover three additional bedrooms and the primary suite. The primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, dual sinks, a large walk-in shower, and a separate bathtub. The upstairs hallway hosts a laundry room, a small desk area, and a balcony overlooking the entry.Step into the backyard, a picturesque oasis with multiple covered areas for entertaining, a stunning paver patio, and low-maintenance artificial turf. An impressive BBQ area enhances the outdoor allure, complemented by an additional storage shed. This residence seamlessly combines style, functionality, and outdoor charm for an unparalleled living experience.   The community boasts a beautiful pool with an additional kiddie pool, kids splash pad area, along with a community park featuring a soccer field and baseball diamond! You do not want to miss out on this opportunity!
